12 Hours Ago “This morning again, I will be returning to the CIID office to pursue the struggle to get Marshal Abubakar freed from illegal and unjust imprisonment. I will be at police unit by 9am. As I have stated, Ned Nwoko acting Buhari’s regime script through the AGF, Abubakar Malami to frame me with further frivolous charges because the treasonable felony charge has practically fallen apart and my recent popular declaration for the Presidency they had wanted to stop by arresting me and harassing me with the police. “The police hierarchy is in his pocket and it will go to any length to violate the rights of Nigerian citizens because of the corrupt relationship with Mr. Nwoko.”